narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Take it. One doesn't get the opportunity to be taught by such professors everyday.
I would recommend this class. If you are interested in the topic, or just want an overview, it will be really helpful. Readings are relevant and it doesn't waste your time.
Good small lecture/seminar. Mainly lecture-style classes with opportunities to ask questions. Professor Wilkinson is extremely knowledgeable and helpful.
The course had a lot of great reading assignments and you will come out having learned a lot if you do even half of them.
